{"tid":2333593,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"中國 McDonald’s 推出期間限定「OREO x SPAM 午餐肉」漢堡","createTime":"2020-12-20T14:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T11:17:01.000Z","uid":1121,"like":2,"dislike":95,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b00e48f2ba3f060d922cdd65d34e0173d6d02ca2","tid":2333593,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53Vo5Gh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F53Vo5Gh.jpg&h=e7351e4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不只日本 McDonald&rsquo;s 時常推出令人眼睛為之一亮的全新產品，中國 McDonald&rsquo;s 過往也曾帶來許多有趣的餐點，稍早，中國 McDonald&rsquo;s 便正式宣佈將與知名午餐肉品牌 SPAM 合作，推出一款期間限定、名為「給利奧餐肉堡」的全新漢堡。這款「給利奧餐肉堡」使用了 OREO 餅乾碎片、SPAM 午餐肉和 McDonald&rsquo;s 經典的漢堡麵包，將略微煎焦的午餐肉和 OREO 結合，搭配上鹹甜鹹甜的美乃滋，呈現出獨特的味道。<br />\n<br />\n「給利奧餐肉堡」定價為 &yen;13.14 人民幣，僅會在 12 月 21 日發售一天，且限定發售 40 萬份，售完為止，有興趣的各位不妨多加留意。"},{"pid":"1184ee302d916fa7869590091850326d5fc881fd","tid":2333593,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:15:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2020/12/mcdonalds-china-spam-oreo-burger-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2020%2F12%2Fmcdonalds-china-spam-oreo-burger-news&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PISVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=a683a78f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2020/12/mcdonalds-china-spam-oreo-burger-news</a>"},{"pid":"ec6667cd3e81f2d63e56a033b0e4e7fb0dc9c733","tid":2333593,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:16:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc08ea01f30d1c720d2b25a5e3ec0731103f372","tid":2333593,"uid":61882,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:17:48.000Z","msg":"痴撚線公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28de95fb8ae2fe661394741425f080fb9ab6d61","tid":2333593,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc